---
title: Beef Meatball Satay with Green Beans and Carrot
description: Also spelled as 'sate' in Indonesia, satay typically consists of skewered meat served with peanut sauce. Meatballs keep it simple whilst a quick sauce makes a deliciously easy way to elevate your dinner and try something new.
